{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"c9j08","text":"Helping tax payers when they're due a refund","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fv94u","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3g0dj","text":"Discovery","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9vt32","text":"Some UK businesses collect Value Added Tax on the goods they sell. Those same businesses also pay VAT on some of the things they buy. When the balance falls in the business favour, HMRC will repay the difference.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7hjrh","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dne20","text":"What's the user need?","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c48ta","text":"Our researcher, Kathy, led on several activities to better understand our users. Combining helpline data with user and stakeholder interviews she identified clear needs:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4fj9c","text":"Tell users how they'd get their repayment.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":3,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6f5f","text":"Tell users when they'd get their repayment.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":4,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e4fgt","text":"Tell users about any delay and inform them how to fix it.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":5,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1g0v","text":"Tell users if HMRC had used repayments to offset other debt.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":2,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a9ekd","text":"Tell users when HMRC had sent repayment.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":4,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5u6bm","text":"What's the business need?","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ci0cb","text":"In 2018, fifty thousand people called asking \"where's my VAT repayment?\".  This demand meant that HMRC was spending £1.3 million yearly in telephony costs. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"hvb3","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4qer3","text":"If a user hadn't supplied bank details, HMRC had to send a cheque. This cost HMRC a further £1.7 million per year.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3o6lv","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"413pe","text":"Saving £3 million a year from the public purse was the ultimate goal of the VAT repayment project.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ap9gr","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4oe4l","text":"What's the current experience?","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"at3af","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}